 our business. With over 100 channels and 2000 video-on-demand content, StarTimes brings loads of exciting entertainment from series, local and foreign movies, music, news, kiddies, documentaries to live sports events. While Warris airs every day at 8:30pm on ST Yoruba and 8:15pm on ST Dadinkowa, the Genral’s Daughter airs daily at 7:40pm on ST Novela E Plus on StarTimes. Vanguard In an obvious move to improve on its entertainment offerings for its growing number of subscribers, leading digital pay-TV company, StarTimes has announced the addition of a new stylish telenovela channel ‘Nina Novelas’ for the delight of television viewers across Africa. Speaking on the content offering, the head of media… March 22, 2020 In "Entertainment" The new exciting Telenovela ‘Battleground’ that has been making waves on DSVT platform since its inception, May 2017 has continued to delight and wow its audience every weeknight with interesting episode after episode. November 22, 2017 In "Entertainment" Veteran actor, Richard Mofe-Damijo, fondly called RMD, has given an interesting insight  into the close bond  he shares with screen darling, Ego Boyo, saying “ she represents female side of what I present for male actors in Nigeria.” April 21, 2018 In "Entertainment"